{"tid":2174753,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭生賣埋鮑魚，花膠 ，花菇麵！！","createTime":"2020-08-26T05:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T09:23:37.000Z","uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"65a6f053c37a210c960a340103959ae33326d42f","tid":2174753,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:43:54.000Z","msg":"【時代冰室 台灣&bull;手工拌麵】<br />\n<br />\n🧳旅行癮發 🍜 掛住當地美食  😣又唔知幾時先🛫飛到？<br />\n時代冰室 新出 💁🏻新產品 幫你止止癮 💪🏻頂住先！<br />\n<br />\n期間限定 🍝蔥油肉燥手工拌麵<br />\n仲配上 🖐🏻5款滋味配搭😋 <br />\n1️⃣滷水雞髀 <br />\n2️⃣滷水雙飛雞翼 <br />\n3️⃣滷水髀翼雙飛<br />\n4️⃣堅&bull;鮑魚花膠花菇<br />\n5️⃣韓豬&bull;黯然叉燒<br />\n<br />\n👀你冇睇錯！ 又鮑魚 又花膠 又花菇 都係＄62！！😱😱😱<br />\n仲有得配 近期🔥大熱嘅 🇰🇷韓豬叉燒<br />\n<br />\n*圖片只供參考<br />\n*11：30後供應<br />\n*數量有限，售完即止<br />\n*疫情期間，請留意店舖截單及營業時間<br />\n*個別分店或因應實際供應情況有所更改，恕不另行通知。不便之處，敬請見諒！🙇🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n*如有任何爭議，時代冰室 保留最終決定權。🙇🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得個女咁靚  日日食都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先天優勢"},{"pid":"5a028d2015ca41951866f1a51fb49ad7221a808e","tid":2174753,"uid":299794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又是你"},{"pid":"2966a5b282d5f33fef022e651c83fc043385dda1","tid":2174753,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:55:01.000Z","msg":"想要蕭生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07113e3ba5b249ca42d571b690be868865e991bf","tid":2174753,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a028d2015ca41951866f1a51fb49ad7221a808e","tid":2174753,"uid":299794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又是你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:55:32.000Z","msg":"訂閱左就有  最新蕭析"},{"pid":"60970cb76def1f63cefc6be9e7838e6a923a3948","tid":2174753,"uid":370202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep